column2: "Looks like something was dragged here. And there are small footprints, too."
"But it looks like they ran off in a hurry. I wonder why..."
"Hmmm, if they were already in this area, then I wonder if we'll be able to find them."
"It's too early to give up! Let's keep looking!"
"<%me>, would you mind sticking around a bit longer?"
